title: Ep 16: You're Not Mature, You're Old
itunes:title: Ep 16: You're Not Mature, You're Old
description: Welcome back to Shannon’s kitchen for episode 2, where she tells us about the time she skipped the Super Bowl for her pregnant best friend (#loyalty), her recent trip to LA, and feeling old… or… ummm… “mature.” Autumn titties is back and has the nose of a hound dog on a hunt apparently. What's the update with WiFi guy?  What to do if you find yourself in a toxic friendship? Where does Shannon see herself in 5 years and much more on episode 2 of Probably a Podcast.
